sql:
SELECT COUNT(*) AS active_documents_count
FROM transaction_documents
WHERE is_active = 1;

external_knowledge:
- The current year refers to the year in which the query is being executed; 
- The start and end of the year refer to January 1st and December 31st of the current year, respectively; 
- Active budget refers to a budget with is_active = 1.

